{"_id":"015f9g1tt1g9f510","name":"Blessing of the Sea","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","scenarioSlug":"a-soldiers-duty","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"165","contentKey":"scenario-gift.a-soldiers-duty.blessing-of-the-sea","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":9,"folderName":"A Soldier’s Duty","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"Bendición del mar","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> demostrar al Hada del Mar tu intención de hacer algo por el pobre Enar.</p><p>Estás bendecido por la poderosa Hada del Mar y, por lo tanto, las aptitudes relacionadas con el mar no tienen ningún efecto sobre ti. Obtienes 2 Éxitos adicionales en todas las pruebas de defensa que hagas para defenderte de un don, hechizo o acción realizada con un descriptor que incluya la palabra mar.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - A Soldier’s Duty","requirements":"demostrar al Hada del Mar tu intención de hacer algo por el pobre Enar.","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty"},"scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"169"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Prove to the Sea Fairy your intention to do something for poor Enar.</p><p>You are blessed by the mighty Sea Fairy and therefore sea-related abilities have no effect on you. You receive 2 Additional Successes on each Defense Check you make to defend yourself against a Gift, spell, or action made using a Descriptor that includes the word sea.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - A Soldier’s Duty","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"A Soldier’s Duty","source":"A Soldier’s Duty","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.a-soldiers-duty.blessing-of-the-sea","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","scenarioSlug":"a-soldiers-duty","sourceDirectory":"a-soldiers-duty","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Prove to the Sea Fairy your intention to do something for poor Enar.","limitations":""},"sort":900000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"0132lc3xx3cl2310","name":"Art of Command","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","scenarioSlug":"a-soldiers-duty","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"165","contentKey":"scenario-gift.a-soldiers-duty.art-of-command","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":10,"folderName":"A Soldier’s Duty","specialFor":"","translations":{"es":{"name":"El arte del mando","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> resistir un asalto de Enar luchando junto a Andersen.</p><p>Has podido observar a un buen líder y saber cómo perfeccionar tus estrategias. Una vez por escena, puedes dar una orden a uno de tus aliados y, si intentan cumplirla, recibirán 2 Éxitos adicionales en cualquier prueba.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - A Soldier’s Duty","requirements":"resistir un asalto de Enar luchando junto a Andersen.","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty"},"scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"169"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> Withstand an onslaught from Enar by fighting alongside Andersen.</p><p>You’ve observed a good leader and figured out how to hone your strategies. Once per Scene, you can give an order to one of your allies and if they try to carry it out, they will receive 2 Additional Successes to any Check.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - A Soldier’s Duty","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"A Soldier’s Duty","source":"A Soldier’s Duty","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.a-soldiers-duty.art-of-command","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","scenarioSlug":"a-soldiers-duty","sourceDirectory":"a-soldiers-duty","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"Withstand an onslaught from Enar by fighting alongside Andersen.","limitations":""},"sort":1000000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"00gua571175aug00","name":"Coral of the Sea Fairy (Special Gift for Marina the Sea Explorer)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/ui/icon_gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","scenarioSlug":"a-soldiers-duty","source":"Broken Tales - Core Rulebook.pdf","pages":"165","contentKey":"scenario-gift.a-soldiers-duty.coral-of-the-sea-fairy","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":11,"folderName":"A Soldier’s Duty","specialFor":"Marina the Sea Explorer","translations":{"es":{"name":"Coral del Hada del Mar (don especial para Marina, la Exploradora del Mar)","system":{"description":"<h3>Don de escenario</h3><p><strong>Requisito:</strong> matar al Hada del Mar.</p><p>Eliminaste a esa odiosa hada y encerraste su alma en un trozo de coral. Ahora su poder es tuyo. Puedes usar 1 Contador de tesoro para desbloquear este don mientras dure el escenario. Gasta 1 Soma para aprovechar el poder del Coral y elige uno de los siguientes efectos. 1. Agua de vida: un objetivo recupera 1 Herida. 2. La furia del mar: el agua del mar lo engulle todo, barriendo todas las amenazas. Aquellos que se encuentren a menos de 9 metros deben superar una prueba de defensa contra NO Difícil 7 para evitar ser arrollados y arrastrados por las olas, sufriendo 1 Herida. 3. Las olas del mar: puedes viajar a cualquier punto del mar en un radio de 10 kilómetros. Este desplazamiento es instantáneo y, si lo deseas, puede llevar hasta a 2 sujetos contigo. Las criaturas marinas perciben lo que has hecho y te atacarán sin dudarlo para intentar liberar el alma del Hada del Mar.</p>","notes":"Don de escenario - A Soldier’s Duty","requirements":"matar al Hada del Mar.","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty"},"scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","source":"Broken Tales - Manual Básico.pdf","pages":"169"}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p><strong>Requirement:</strong> To kill the Sea Fairy.</p><p>You dispatched that hateful fairy and harnessed her soul in a lump of coral. Now her power is yours. You can use 1 Treasure Token to unlock this Gift for the duration of the Scenario. Spend 1 Soma to tap into the Coral’s power and choose one of the following effects. 1. Water of Life: A target recovers 1 Wound. 2. The Fury of the Sea: The water of the sea engulfs everything, sweeping away all threats. Those who are within 30 feet must pass a Defense Check against OL Hard 7 to avoid being overwhelmed by the waves and being thrown away, suffering 1 Wound. 3. The Waves of the Sea: You can travel to any point of the sea within 6 miles. This shift is instantaneous and you can take up to 2 subjects with you. Sea creatures sense what you have done and will attack you without hesitation to try to free the soul of the Fairy.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - A Soldier’s Duty","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"A Soldier’s Duty","source":"A Soldier’s Duty","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.a-soldiers-duty.coral-of-the-sea-fairy","scenario":"A Soldier’s Duty","scenarioSlug":"a-soldiers-duty","sourceDirectory":"a-soldiers-duty","tags":["scenario-gift"],"requirements":"To kill the Sea Fairy.","limitations":""},"sort":1100000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332107,"modifiedTime":1784370086875,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
